metadata.name: Red Rose
metadata.description:
Who are the inhabitants of the planet Earth in future? 
In a world where robots grow iron flowers, is finding a small rose a sign for presence of living beings? who knows!  
Come with me.  
There is an imaginary world that I will take you there with me, where Robots are inhabitances on the Earth.  
4423 x 5257 px  
300 DPI
